{
  "stem": "8212.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My sister went to Israel after the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they came only a few years later.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They must have found out through the Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And mostly my uncle, who lived in Switzerland, probably found out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm sure they did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm sure they did, but-- and I only realized last year, when I found my grandfather's grave in Vienna, that my uncle must have put this in 1947-- the stone.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When he found out that my grandfather's ashes were sent back, he must have put that stone.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I discovered it only last year.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They never talked to us about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was so surprised and touched to find this stone in Vienna at the Jewish cemetery, the part that is totally neglected.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There's part of the cemetery that has beautiful stones and everything, from people who died before the war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But all the people that died afterwards, where the ashes were sent back-- they are just in some kind of a potter's field.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And some have-- have nothing at all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when I went back to Vienna last year and tried to find out, I realized only then that, after we left in 1939 and my grandparents stayed alone in Vienna, my grandfather was sent to Buchenwald, just a few months after we left, in 1939.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after a few months, he died there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they sent his ashes back to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At this point, apparently, my grandmother was still in Vienna till 1942, for another two years.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the address they gave me was an address that I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they explained to me that they put people together in apartments-- lots of people-- for two years.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And she was only then sent to Theresienstadt, and died in Theresienstadt in 1942.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
